---
/**
 * Brand wordmark "PROJECT FUSION" as a static vector graphic.
 *
 * The lettering was outlined once from the licensed Nasalization OTF (kept
 * outside the repo) into a single merged path — the Typodermic desktop EULA
 * permits static graphic images, but not shipping the font itself (§2/§4).
 * Tracking 0.06em is baked into the geometry. The display size follows Chris'
 * lockup design (docs/design/assets/logo-fusion-wordmark.svg): cap height =
 * 0.673 × flame height, i.e. 16.15px next to the 24px LogoFlame; SiteHeader
 * scales both down on narrow phones. Fills use `currentColor`, so the mark
 * inherits the text color.
 */
---

